<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I think that Verant requiring people to upgrade to Direct X 7.0a was completely reasonable.  The cost to upgrade a video card and/or RAM is minimal.  $200 is not an unreasonable amount of money to pay for a good video card and more RAM.<P>Also, by upgrading your hardware you are not only enabling your PC to continue to run EverQuest; you are also enabling your PC to run other CURRENT games.<P>Basically people just like to gripe about things......  get over it!<P>------------------<BR>Qaedain of Felwithe<BR>Wizard
