I have a really high-end gaming system, Athlon 750, 256MB PC133 5ns SDRAM, GeForce2GTS, SBLive! etc.  There isn't a game out on the market that isnt playable on this setup.  I, personally, am VERY grateful of the upgrade.  <P>Prior to the upgrade I could not walk around Warsliks with clipping all the way up, or even halfway up, it had to be all the way down, even in 640x480.  Also, the graphics (from lack of mip-mapping) were horrible.<P>Now, after the upgrade to DirectX 7.0, performace has significantly increased, as well was graphic quality, since mip-mapping now works properly with my GeForce.  I had no problems whatsoever after patch, and I, for one, am very grateful for the upgrade.<P>------------------<BR>Krystalis Efyu<BR>Iksar Monk <BR>Cazic-Thule
